            Shuvu Batta,
          
          
            21 March 2020
          
        </p>
      
      
        <p class="desc">The discovery that an Amazon worker in Queens had tested positive for coronavirus sparked work stoppages which shut the processing facility Thursday night.</p>
      

      

    
    

  

  

  

  

  

  




